netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain.descriptor

Class DomainNameAvailabilityDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain.descriptor.DomainNameAvailabilityDescriptor

  • public class DomainNameAvailabilityDescriptor
extends java.lang.Object
    Descriptor for a domain name hinted availability operation. This is passed to the getHintedAvailability function on the Domains API.
